title: SUBMIT QUESTIONS !!!  For a Q & A. What's on your mind? (Limited Time Video)
description:
This is just a quick video to gather questions for a Q and A in two weeks. There will not be a live feed for this. Simply submit your questions below. Watch the video for instructions. Thanks. THIS VIDEO WILL ONLY BE ACTIVE FOR A WEEK.


And remember you can contribute to The Anadromist through PayPal here.
